It comes with all the OEM goodies, plus: 

Four (4) metal, ten-shot magazines (one OEM and three new aftermarkets); 
Two OEM barrels (one 5" & one 3.42"); 
Stabilizer assembly / frame extension for 5" barrel; 
Two grip-frame back straps; 
All the barrel-change tools included; 
Three extra front sights for different barrels; and  
OEM Walther black plastic storage case. 

WTS for $475. Prefer to sell either FTF w/ Bill of Sale to FL CWL holder or handle through FFL. Also, WTT for GLOCKS, Beretta Nano or Ruger LC9. Tell me what you've got and maybe we can do a trade. Thanks for looking.
